# 14. Explain Watchdog Timer

A watchdog timer detects system hangs or communication failures.

---

## Example

PLC expects heartbeat every 1 second.

If heartbeat missing:

* Trigger fault
* Stop motor
* Raise alarm

---

## Uses

* Communication supervision
* Safety monitoring
* System recovery

